node.text:
Chillax... It's TGIF!!! And a great news to all Singaporeans. We are official entering phrase 2 of opening up our economy. ♥️👍🏻
.
While it's still a way to go to full recovery and obviously it's still not the time for party mode, but it's worth celebrating the mood. 😍👍🏻
.
Since is a happy day, randomly share two secrets with everyone today... 🤫👌🏻🤣
.
1) During the circuit breaker lockdown, for the past 2.5 months, I dont have to wash my pants at all! Only wear the top shirt for online classes, hence I save a lot of water and detergent. 🤣🤣🤣
.
2) During this photoshoot at @thetaarasmalaysia with @berjayahotelsresorts I didnt on that tap at all. It was a photoshoot! Haha sad me didnt have the time to enjoy the bath... I was there for an hour, cold and hungry... 🥺
.
Just for laugh... enjoy the weekend & fathers day. .
Remember to take precautions and stay safe! ♥️👍🏻
Thank you for sharing🤗. Do visit us again soon 🤗
@kimichan75 hahaha no not daddy yet hahahahahaha but happy fathers day... cos it's a god celebration for all fathers in the world 😍👍
😂😂😂 so, in Singapore, the father's day is also the third Sunday in June..... nice to know, because here in Argentina too 😊  Should I say for you? 😋
@sophialkt yea I really miss those days 😍👍
Awwwww our first ever trip together 😍 Hope to go back to the Taaras with you soon ❤️❤️❤️
😂😂😂😂 you take a bath with no bubble soap...still so good looking❤️saranghae
@angelathegrace hahaha happy phrase 2 hahaha so many people everywhere... am happy to see everything alive again 😍👍
hey buddy.. ahem ahem, you just very publicly announced 2 secrets you gathered over this covid lockdown 🙊 ... good luck to you 👍 & TGIF! 🤣🤣🤣🤣🤣
@zuzunien the other side??? The mountains? Lol
i wan i wan sit the other side.can or not
@bohdana_morson thank you so much and hope you continue improve and deepen your language skills. U gotta start traveling asia once covid19 is over to practice those newly acquired skills

Have a wonderful weekend and a happy Father’s Day. I wish you and everyone peace and good health. During the coronavirus outbreak, I learned more about Black history (global as well) and I expanded my vocabulary and grammar in Korean. I read more books. You are gifted. Thank you. 👩‍🏫💪👩‍🎓 #knowledgeispower #languageisthenewcurrency #languagelearning #blackhistoryiseveryday
@cafetini hahahahahahaha I didnt know that's what u do 🤣🤣🤣🤣🤣
Can drink the water & keep ur stomach full 😜😂
@zakroams it is a beautiful place to chillax... 😍
Damn this looks like a seriously good place to relax
